name: Handicap-Accessible-Executive-Jr.-Suite-Executive-Jr.-Suite---View-from-Sleeper-Sofa
caption: Executive Jr. Suite - View from Sleeper Sofa
description: This suite includes queen size bed, living area with sleeper sofa, arm chair, and tv.
alt: In the right corner of the room, a queen bed is nestled to the right of a double window. A tv rests on the wall between this window and another window, hanging above a small dresser. In front of the second window sits an arm chair. The arm chair, along with a couch perpendicular to it, surround a glass coffee table.
